{"questionId":"2718966","questionHtml":"<p>Use integration to find <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Var</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo>)</mo></math> in terms of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>uses <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Var</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">E</mi><mo>(</mo><msup><mi>X</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>)</mo><mo>-</mo><msup><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">E</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>Var</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><munderover><mo>∫</mo><mi>a</mi><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>a</mi></mrow></munderover><mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">d</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mfrac><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mrow><mn>6</mn><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac></mfenced><mi>a</mi><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>a</mi></mrow></msubsup><mo>-</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>13</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>-</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>a</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mf